      <title>伦敦黑色出租车司机向 Uber 提起 2.5 亿英镑诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/uber-hit-with-250-million-suit-from-london-s-black-cab-drivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦数千名黑色出租车司机起诉优步科技公司，要求赔偿数亿英镑，指控其在首都非法运营。]]></description>
